## Deployment Strategy

We use **Salesforce DX (SFDX) + Metadata API** with Git for version control.

---

## sfdx-project.json

```json
{
    \"packageDirectories\": [
        {
            \"path\": \"force-app\",
            \"default\": true
        }
    ],
    \"name\": \"AI-Powered-Job-Recruitment\",
    \"namespace\": \"\",
    \"sfdcLoginUrl\": \"https://login.salesforce.com\",
    \"sourceApiVersion\": \"59.0\"
}
```

---

## package.xml (Manifest)

```xml
<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>
<Package xmlns=\"http://soap.sforce.com/2006/04/metadata\">
    <types>
        <members>Job__c</members>
        <members>Candidate__c</members>
        <members>Application__c</members>
