## End-User Documentation

### 1. Logging In
1. Visit `https://<your-org>.lightning.force.com`
2. Enter username & password
3. Switch to \"Recruitment Hub\" app from App Launcher

---

### 2. Creating a Job
1. Click **Jobs** tab → **New**
2. Fill in:
   - Job Title
   - Department
   - Min/Max Salary
   - Required Skills
   - Job Description
3. Set Status = `Open` → Save
4. Note the auto-generated Job Number (e.g., `JOB-0001`)

---

### 3. Adding a Candidate
1. Click **Candidates** tab → **New**
2. Enter Name, Email, Phone, Skills, Experience
3. Add Resume Link (Google Drive / SharePoint)
4. Save — system auto-checks for duplicates

---

### 4. Creating an Application
1. From the Candidate record → Related → **Applications** → New
2. Select Job
3. Set Status = `New`
4. Save — **AI Match Score** auto-populates within seconds

---

### 5. Reviewing AI Match
1. Open Application record
2. View \"AI Match Analysis\" card (right panel)
3. Green badge = Strong match (≥75)
4. Click \"Re-run AI Analysis\" if needed

---

### 6. Scheduling Interview
1. From Application → Related → **Interviews** → New
2. Set Interview Date, Interviewer, Round
3. Save — email auto-sent to candidate

---

### 7. Submitting Feedback
1. Interviewer opens Interview record
2. Fills Feedback + Result (Pass/Fail/On-Hold)
3. If Pass → Application status auto-shortlisted

---

### 8. Creating & Approving Offer
1. From Application → Related → **Offers** → New
2. Enter Offered Salary, Joining Date
3. Click \"Submit for Approval\"
4. HR Manager receives email → Approves/Rejects
5. Candidate notified automatically

---

## Admin Documentation

### Maintaining Profiles
- **Setup → Users → Profiles → [Edit]**

### Editing Validation Rules
- **Setup → Object Manager → [Object] → Validation Rules**

### Managing Flows
- **Setup → Process Automation → Flows**

### Monitoring Agentforce
- **Setup → Einstein → Agent Studio → Logs**

---

## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| AI Score = 0 | Check Apex logs, Agentforce credentials |
| Email not sent | Verify Email Deliverability (Setup → Deliverability) |
| Approval not triggered | Check entry criteria, record status |
| Duplicate not blocked | Confirm Matching Rule is Active |

---

## Training Resources

- Video walkthroughs (10 mins each per role)
- PDF user guide
- In-app guidance via Salesforce Lightning Walkthroughs
- Slack channel: `#recruitment-hub-support`
