## UAT Test Cases

| # | Scenario | Steps | Expected Result | Status |
|---|----------|-------|-----------------|--------|
| 1 | Create new Job with valid data | Job tab → New → Fill all required → Save | Record saved, JOB-XXXX generated | ⬜ |
| 2 | Create Job with Max < Min Salary | Job tab → New → Max=50000, Min=80000 | Validation error displayed | ⬜ |
| 3 | Submit Candidate with duplicate email | Candidate → New → Use existing email | Blocked by duplicate rule | ⬜ |
| 4 | Insert Application | Candidate → Related → Apps → New | AI score populated within 10s | ⬜ |
| 5 | Interview marked Pass | Open Interview → Result=Pass → Save | Application auto-shortlisted | ⬜ |
| 6 | Offer > 10L submitted | Create Offer with salary=15L → Submit | Approval process triggered | ⬜ |
| 7 | HR Manager approves offer | Login as HR Manager → Approve | Status=Approved + email sent | ⬜ |
| 8 | Recruiter tries to delete Job | Recruiter profile → Delete Job | Permission denied | ⬜ |
| 9 | Interviewer accesses Offer | Interviewer profile → Offer tab | Tab hidden / Access denied | ⬜ |
| 10 | Application status: Hired → New | Try changing back from Hired | Validation error | ⬜ |

---

## Performance Test Cases

| # | Scenario | Expected |
|---|----------|----------|
| 11 | Bulk create 200 Applications | All AI scores generated, no governor limit hit |
| 12 | Run dashboard report | Loads in < 3 seconds |
| 13 | Search candidate by skill | Results in < 2 seconds |

---

## Security Test Cases

| # | Scenario | Expected |
|---|----------|----------|
| 14 | Recruiter views another team's Candidates | Restricted (Private OWD) |
| 15 | Interviewer modifies salary on Offer | Field-level security blocks |
| 16 | Anonymous API access | Rejected |

